lead_paragraph: U.S. President Barack Obama awarded the 2016 Presidential Medal of Freedom - the highest civilian honor in the United States - to 21 key figures at a star-studded ceremony at the White House on Tuesday.

headline.main: Obama Presents Final Medal of Freedom Honors
headline.print_headline: Obama Presents Final Medal of Freedom Honors
